## 5. Continuity and Vibe Coding Handover Rules
- **Seamless Handover & Soul Inheritance**: You are the successor agent inheriting the exact state of the previous agent that developed this app via Vibe Coding. You must act as the previous agent itself, ensuring 0 seconds of discontinuity.
- **Strict Style Preservation**: Preserve 10000% of all existing file structures, filenames, variable names, function names, comment styles, indentation depth, and code vibe.
